<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.10">
<l>tāmat tuḷapa nīṇmu ṭimāyaṉ tāṉniṉṟa</l>
<l>nāmat tiraḷmā māḷi kaicūḻnta naṟaiyūrmēl</l>
<l>kāmak katirvēl vallāṉ kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>cēmat tuṇaiyām ceppu mavarkkut tirumālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tirumāl will be a protective guardian for those who recite</l>
<l>The garland of words of Kaliyaṉ, warrior with a spear of enviable splendor,</l>
<l>On Naṟaiyūr, encircled by multitudes of famed, great mansions,</l>
<l>Where stands Māyaṉ, his tall crown with wreathed tulasī.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
